{"tid":693627,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【震撼全港馬迷】雷神莫雷拉宣佈 季後離開香港","createTime":"2018-06-07T15:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T15:49:39.000Z","uid":112485,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebe759ce9fd54c088f2fe26fcc5f06a331ae048","tid":693627,"uid":112485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"就在馬會於明日（8日）公佈來季獲發牌騎師前夕，近三年均稱霸香港馬壇的莫雷拉，宣佈撤出香江的驚人消息。<br />\n<br />\n正值停賽的莫雷拉表示已向牌照委員會，撤回已提出的來季騎師牌照申請，並於今個本港馬季完結（7月15日）後轉赴日本發展，從而結束在港接近五年的策騎生涯。<br />\n<br />\n人稱雷神的莫雷拉祖籍巴西，現年34歲。來港發展一段時間，他是星洲冠軍騎師，並於13年10月20日起，以馬會騎師身份在港上陣<br />\n<br />\n當日跑谷中日馬，雷神原本一路無馬贏，手風欠順。最終他戰至最尾第十場，憑當時隸屬告達理馬房的賽駒「魅力星」（已退役）贏馬，就此展開不平凡的香港職業騎師生涯。<br />\n<br />\n當季雷神在港勝出97場頭馬，不敵潘頓在騎師榜排第二，翌季（14/15年度馬季）他以145場頭馬擊敗所有對手，首奪本港騎師冠軍寶座。<br />\n<br />\n往後兩季即15至17年度馬季，雷神分別以168及170Win，再兩度榮膺香港冠軍騎師<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180607&amp;s=10860680&amp;a=58291092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180607%26s%3D10860680%26a%3D58291092&d=ANaRpzbWz%2BOUP63y54PQsWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=e2edc35e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180607%26s%3D10860680%26a%3D58291092&h=45ffc7a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180607&amp;s=10860680&amp;a=58291092</a>"},{"pid":"df421fe782dd1309ca35ea483581955cbcf9f983","tid":693627,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"1500"},{"pid":"fea25fa6d6b1ae6ffc50d3eab2c8aaa1abae644e","tid":693627,"uid":58346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db80fa977e1d4415d734acdc57e7663c9926162e","tid":693627,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:37:25.000Z","msg":"潘狗實拉馬拉得重勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37dab13f1f5b4027c48020870817418054db0a75","tid":693627,"uid":98942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74705d13f8a38f70d61a2603e6518e611c9a3c1a","tid":693627,"uid":34352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"又比班澳洲黑幫惡哂，迫害馬迷"},{"pid":"861c173b5ec38ddf0803e67b0225f880f059db81","tid":693627,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"小一個雷神<br />\n多一個俊神"}]}